FORMAT: 1A
HOST: https://www.printavo.com

# Printavo API
This JSON-based API is used to access information in your Printavo account. Printavo is the simplest way for screen-printing, embroidering and promotional product shops to manage their business.

###### Rate Limiting
For API requests, we allow a limit of 10 requests for every 5 seconds by IP address or by user login email


# Group Sessions

## Sessions [/api/{version}/sessions]
Login and Logout

+ Parameters

   + version (required, string, `v1`) - API version.

### Login [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

  +  Attributes (object)
      + email (required, string)
      + password (required, string)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

   + Headers

            Connection: keep-alive

   + Body

            {
              "email": "test@example.com",
              "id": 1,
              "token": "6WfC-lLQNVs_qGIe93iutw"
            }

### Logout [DELETE]

+ Request (application/json)

  +  Attributes (object)
      + email (required, string)
      + token (required, string)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

   + Headers

            Connection: keep-alive
            
