# Group Users

## Users collection [/api/{version}/users{?email}{?token}{?page}{?per_page}]
Actions on the Users resource

+ Parameters

    + version (required, string, `v1`) - API version.
    + email (required, string, `test@example.com`) - User email
    + token (required, string, `1dofnewoi233`) - Login token
    + page (optional, string) - Number of page.
        + Default: `1`
    + per_page (optional, string) - Number of users per page.
        + Default: `20`

### Users Index [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Connection: keep-alive

    + Body

            {
              "meta": {
                "page": 1,
                "per_page": 20,
                "total_count": 4,
                "total_pages": 1
              },
              "data": [
