# Group Messages

## Messages collection [/api/{version}/messages{?email}{?token}{?page}{?per_page}]
Actions on the Message resource

+ Parameters

    + version (required, string, `v1`) - API version.
    + email (required, string, `test@example.com`) - User email
    + token (required, string, `1dofnewoi233`) - Login token
    + page (optional, string) - Number of page.
        + Default: `1`
    + per_page (optional, string) - Number of customers per page.
        + Default: `25`

### Messages Index [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Connection: keep-alive

    + Body

            {
            "meta": 
              {
                "page": 1,
                "per_page": 20,
                "total_count": 4,
                "total_pages": 1
              },
            "data": 
              [
                {
                  "from": "queenie@quitzon.name",
                  "to": "kyla_abernathy@vandervort.name",
                  "subject": nil,
                  "created_at": "2017-08-07T10:38:23.616-07:00",
                  "updated_at": "2017-08-07T10:38:23.616-07:00",
                  "user_id": 1,
                  "messageable_id": 1,
                  "cc_invoice_creator": false,
                  "messageable_type": "Order",
                  "to_user": true,
                  "formatted_delivery_status": "pending",
                  "bounce_error": nil,
                  "reply_text": nil,
                  "text": "Ruh ahuma ooma?"
                }
              ]
            }

### Message Create [POST]

+  Attributes (object)
      + order_id (required, number)
      + email_message (optional, object)
        + to (required, string)
        + text (required, string)
        + subject (optional, string)
        + cc_invoice_creator (optional, boolean)

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Accept-Charset: utf-8
            Connection: keep-alive
    + Body

            {
              "email_message":
                {
                  "to": "elsie@cronin.name",
                  "text": "Some text",
                  "subject": "Subject",
                  "cc_invoice_creator": true
                },
              "order_id": 1
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Connection: keep-alive

    + Body

            {
              "from": "eda.pouros@corkery.io",
              "to": "elsie@cronin.name",
              "subject": "Wuckert, Schneider and Eichmann sent you a message",
              "created_at": "2017-08-07T12:08:37.364-07:00",
              "updated_at": "2017-08-07T12:08:37.364-07:00",
              "user_id": 1,
              "messageable_id": 1,
              "text": "Some text",
              "messageable_type": "Order",
              "state": "linked",
              "to_user": false,
              "delivery_status": nil,
              "bounce_error": nil,
              "reply_text": nil,
              "cc_invoice_creator": nil
            }

# Group Customers

## Customers collection [/api/{version}/customers{?email}{?token}{?page}{?per_page}{?sort_column}{?direction}{?exclude_sub_customers}]
Actions on the Customers resource

+ Parameters

    + version (required, string, `v1`) - API version.
    + email (required, string, `test@example.com`) - User email
    + token (required, string, `1dofnewoi233`) - Login token
    + page (optional, string) - Number of page.
        + Default: `1`
    + per_page (optional, string) - Number of customers per page.
        + Default: `25`
    + sort_column (optional, string) - Column to sort on
        + Default: `first_name`
    + direction (optional, string) - Direction to sort
        + Default: `asc`
    + exclude_sub_customers (optional, boolean) - Exclude sub customers from results
        + Default: false

