### Customers Search [GET /api/{version}/customers/search{?email}{?token}{?page}{?per_page}{?query}{?sort_column}{?direction}]

+ Parameters

    + version (required, string, `v1`) - API version.
    + email (required, string, `test@example.com`) - User email
    + token (required, string, `1dofnewoi233`) - Login token
    + page (optional, string) - Number of page.
        + Default: `1`
    + per_page (optional, string) - Number of customers per page.
        + Default: `25`
    + query (required, string) - Query to search
    + sort_column (optional, string) - Column to sort on
        + Values: `first_name`, `last_name`, `company`, `email`, `orders_count`, `created_at`, `customer_id`
        + Default: `first_name`
    + direction (optional, string) - Direction to sort
        + Default: `asc`
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Connection: keep-alive

    + Body

            {
