# Group Orders

## Orders collection [/api/{version}/orders{?email}{?token}{?page}{?per_page}{?sort_column}{?direction}{?in_production_after}{?in_production_before}]
Actions on the Orders resource

+ Parameters

    + version (required, string, `v1`) - API version.
    + email (required, string, `test@example.com`) - User email
    + token (required, string, `1dofnewoi233`) - Login token
    + page (optional, string) - Number of page.
        + Default: `1`
    + per_page (optional, string) - Number of orders per page.
        + Default: `25`
    + sort_column (optional, string) - Column to sort on
        + Default: `id`
    + direction (optional, string) - Direction to sort
        + Default: `desc`
    + in_production_after (optional, string) - DateTime to filter on Orders with a due date after the specified DateTime. Format: ISO8601
    + in_production_before (optional, string) - DateTime to filter on Orders with a due date before the specified DateTime. Format: ISO8601
      

