### Orders Search [GET /api/{version}/orders/search{?email}{?token}{?page}{?per_page}{?query}]

+ Parameters

    + version (required, string, `v1`) - API version.
    + email (required, string, `test@example.com`) - User email
    + token (required, string, `1dofnewoi233`) - Login token
    + page (optional, string) - Number of page.
        + Default: `1`
    + per_page (optional, string) - Number of orders per page.
        + Default: `25`
    + query (required, string) - String to search

