# Group Inquiries

## Inquiries collection [/api/{version}/inquiries{?email}{?token}{?page}{?per_page}]
Actions on the Inquiries resource

+ Parameters

    + version (required, string, `v1`) - API version.
    + email (required, string, `test@example.com`) - User email
    + token (required, string, `1dofnewoi233`) - Login token
    + page (optional, string) - Number of page.
        + Default: `1`
    + per_page (optional, string) - Number of inquiries per page.
        + Default: `20`

### Inquiries Index [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Connection: keep-alive

    + Body

            {
              "meta": {
                "page": 1,
                "per_page": 20,
                "total_count": 38,
                "total_pages": 2
              },
              "data": [
                {
                  "id": 2252,
                  "description": "1",
                  "customer_name": "omwylloe",
                  "customer_email": "sample@email.tst",
                  "customer_phone": "555-666-0606",
                  "read": false,
                  "created_at": "2015-05-22T04:02:07-05:00",
                  "updated_at": "2015-05-22T04:02:07-05:00"
                }
              ]
            }

