# Group Preset Task Groups
Properties

| Name | Type | Description |
|:-----|:-----|:------------|
| title |  String | Description/Name of the Preset Task Group |
| preset_tasks_attributes |  Array  | Preset Tasks |
| preset_tasks_attributes[id] | Integer | The id of the Preset Task to update |
| preset_tasks_attributes[task_name] |  String | Description/Name of the Preset Task |
| preset_tasks_attributes[assigned_user_id] |  Integer | Assign this Preset Task to a User via a user_id |
| preset_tasks_attributes[position] |  Integer | Position of the Preset Task |
| preset_tasks_attributes[_destroy] |  Boolean  | Destroy this Task |

  
    
## Preset Task Groups collection [/api/{version}/preset_task_groups{?email}{?token}{?page}{?per_page}]
Actions on the Preset Task Groups resource
      
+ Parameters

    + version (required, string, `v1`) - API version.
    + email (required, string, `test@example.com`) - User email
    + token (required, string, `1dofnewoi233`) - Login token
    + page (optional, integer) - Number of page.
        + Default: `1`
    + per_page (optional, integer) - Number of order statuses per page.
        + Default: `25`

