# Data Structures

## Customer (object)
+ first_name (optional, string)
+ last_name (optional, string)
+ user_id (optional, number)
+ company (required, string)
+ customer_email (optional, string) - Multiple emails can be added using commas.
+ phone (optional, string)
+ extra_notes (optional, string) - Additional notes about the customer.
+ fax (optional, string)
+ tax_exempt (optional, boolean) - Customer tax exempt?. Default: false.
+ tax_resale_num (optional, string) - Resale Number.
+ sales_tax (optional, number) - Sales tax as a percentage. Ex: '8.8'
+ billing_address_attributes (optional, object) - Hash with data for Billing Address.
    + address1 (optional, string)
    + address2 (optional, string)
    + city (optional, string)
    + state (optional, string) - State as the full name. ex: 'Illinois'
    + zip (optional, string)
    + country (optional, string) - Country as 2 digit code. Ex: 'US'
+ shipping_address_attributes (optional, object) - Hash with data for Shipping Address.
    + address1 (optional, string)
    + address2 (optional, string)
    + city (optional, string)
    + state (optional, string) - State as the full name. Ex: 'Illinois'
    + zip (optional, string)
    + country (optional, string) - Country as 2 digit code. Ex: 'US'
+ sub_customers_attributes (optional, object) - Hash with data for SubCustomers.
    + first_name (optional, string)
    + last_name (optional, string)
    + user_id (optional, number)
    + phone (optional, string)
    + email (optional, string)
    + fax (optional, string)

## Product (object)
+ brand (optional, string)
+ style_number (optional, string)
+ style_description (optional, string)
+ color (optional, string)
+ size (optional, string)
+ price_per (optional, number)
+ dozens_price (optional, number)
+ case_price (optional, number)

## Order (object)
+ user_id (required, number)
+ customer_id (required, number)
+ orderstatus_id (required, number)
+ visual_po_number (optional, string)
+ due_date (optional, string) - Production due date with a time component. Format: ISO8601
+ formatted_custom_created_at_date (optional, string) - Custom created at date. Format: MM/DD/YYYY
+ formatted_due_date (optional, string) - Production due date. Format: MM/DD/YYYY
+ formatted_customer_due_date (required, string) - Customer due date. Format: MM/DD/YYYY
+ formatted_invoice_date (optional, string) - Invoice date. Format: MM/DD/YYYY
+ formatted_payment_due_date (optional, string) - Payment due date. Format: MM/DD/YYYY
+ sales_tax (optional, number) - Sales tax as a percentage. Ex: '8.8'
+ discount (optional, number) - Discount as a percentage or amount. Example: 10% = 10.0 or $20 = 15.0.
+ discount_as_percentage (optional, boolean) - Is the discount a percentage? If not then it's a fixed amount. Default: false.
+ order_nickname (optional, string) - Nickname for the order.
+ approved (optional, boolean) - Is the order approved?. Default: false.
+ approved_name (optional, string) - This is mandatory if approved is true.
+ production_notes (optional, string) - Notes visible to user accounts that are logged in.
+ notes (optional, string) - Notes visible to the customer and to user accounts logged in.
+ payment_term_id (optional, number)
+ delivery_method_id (optional, number)
+ delivery_method_id (optional, number)
+ order_addresses_attributes (optional, array)
    + name (required, string) - First two addresses must be 'Customer Billing', 'Customer Shipping'
    + company_name (optional, string)
    + customer_name (optional, string)
    + address1 (optional, string)
    + address2 (optional, string)
    + city (optional, string)
    + state (optional, string) - State as the full name. ex: 'Illinois'
    + zip (optional, string)
    + country (optional, string) - Country as 2 digit code. Ex: 'US'
+ lineitems_attributes (optional, object)
    + style_description (optional, string) - Description of line item
    + style_number (optional, string) - Brand style number
    + color (optional, string)
    + category_id (optional, number) - Category ID
    + size_6m (optional, number) - Size - 6 Months
    + size_12m (optional, number) - Size - 12 Months
    + size_18m (optional, number) - Size - 18 Months
    + size_24m (optional, number) - Size - 24 Months
    + size_2t (optional, number) - Size - 2 Toddler
    + size_3t (optional, number) - Size - 3 Toddler
    + size_4t (optional, number) - Size - 4 Toddler
    + size_5t (optional, number) - Size - 5 Toddler
    + size_yxs (optional, number) - Size - Youth X-Small
    + size_ys (optional, number) - Size - Youth Small
    + size_ym (optional, number) - Size - Youth Medium
    + size_yl (optional, number) - Size - Youth Large
    + size_yxl (optional, number) - Size - Youth X-Large
    + size_xs (optional, number) - Size - X-Small
    + size_s (optional, number) - Size - Small
    + size_m (optional, number) - Size - Medium
    + size_l (optional, number) - Size - Large
    + size_xl (optional, number) - Size - X-Large
    + size_2xl (optional, number) - Size - 2X-Large
    + size_3xl (optional, number) - Size - 3X-Large
    + size_4xl (optional, number) - Size - 4X-Large
    + size_5xl (optional, number) - Size - 5X-Large
    + size_6xl (optional, number) - Size - 6X-Large
    + size_other (optional, number) - Size - General
    + unit_cost (required, number)
    + taxable (optional, boolean) - Is this line item taxed? Default: true
    + images_attributes (optional, object)
        + file_url (required, string) - Image must be uploaded to Filestack.com, ex: "https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/PNvWyfxQRaVhwJgLY8E3"
        + mime_type (required, string) - File type, ex: "image/png"
    + print_locations_attributes (optional, object)
        + details (optional, string)
+ production_notes_files_attributes (optional, object) - Production files are used to store vectorized/digitized files on an Order
    + file_url (required, string) - Image must be uploaded to Filestack.com, ex: "https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/PNvWyfxQRaVhwJgLY8E3"
    + mime_type (required, string) - File type, ex: "image/png"
+ order_fees_attributes (optional, object)
    + amount (required, number)
    + description (optional, string)
    + taxable (optional, boolean) - Is this fee taxable?. Default: false.

## Inquirie (object)
+ description (optional, string)
+ customer_phone (optional, string)
+ customer_email (optional, string)

## Task (object)
+ task_name (optional, string) - Description/Name of the task
+ formatted_due_date (optional, string) - Example: MM/DD/YYYY
+ assigned_user_id (optional, number) - Assign this task to a User
+ taskable_id (optional, number) - Either a Customer or Order ID to attach this task to an order or customer
+ taskable_type (optional, string) - Either 'Order' or 'Customer' to attach this task to an order or customer

## Expense (object)
+ amount (required, number)
+ name (required, string)
+ transaction_date (required, string)

## Expenseupdate (object)
+ amount (optional, number)
+ name (optional, string)
+ transaction_date (optional, string)

## Payment (object)
+ amount (required, number)
+ name (required, string)
+ transaction_date (required, string)
+ order_id (required, number)

## PaymentTerm (object)
+ name (required, string)
+ days (required, number)

## DeliveryMethod (object)
+ name (required, string)
+ archived (optional, boolean)

## BookPayment (object)
+ book
  + amount (required, number)
  + formatted_transaction_date (required, string) - "MM/DD/YYYY"
  + book_category_id (optional, number)
  + name (optional, string)
  + user_generated (optional, string)

## BookPaymentRequest (object)
+ payment_request
  + cc_boolean (optional, boolean) - "Do you want to CC the invoice creator?"
  + cc_recipients (optional, string) - "tim@example.com, jane@example.com"
  + send_email (optional, boolean) - "Would you like to send an email to the customer for this invoice to request the payment?"
  + amount (required, string) - "The amount you'd like to to request, example: '150.25'"
  + account (object)
    + payment_request_template (optional, string) - "The body of the email if you'd like to send an email to the customer"

## Paymentupdate (object)
+ amount (optional, number)
+ name (optional, string)
+ transaction_date (optional, string)

## EmailInvoice (object)
+ order (object)
  + email_to (required, string)
  + cc_invoice_creator (optional, boolean)
  + account (object)
      - invoice_template_subject_line (required, string)
      - invoice_template (required, string)
